stage of trichinellosis in a new epidemic focus in Wielkopolska.
Proceedings of the International Commission of Trichinellosis
No. XXIV. Wiadomosci Parazytologiczne 1997;43:257-63.
3.Bari C DI, Santagada G, Pozio E, Schiraldi O. Epidemiological
research on trichinellosis in Apulia and Basilicata (southern Italy).
Eur J Epidemiol 1990;6:412-5.
4.Egbering O. Observations on the origin and course of a
trichinellosis epidemic [German. Giessen, German Federal Republic:
Department of Veterinary Medicine, Justus-Liebig University, 1988.
5.Ancelle T, Dupouy-Camet J, Desenclos JC, et al. A multifocal
